---
interface Props {
  section: string;
  fallbackBody?: string;
}
const { section, fallbackBody } = Astro.props;
---

{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* CHALLENGES SECTION                                                  */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "challenges" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-4">
    Topstep has <strong>one evaluation step</strong> &mdash; the <strong>Trading Combine</strong>. After passing, traders move directly to an <strong>Express Funded Account</strong> where payouts begin. A <strong>Live Funded Account</strong> is only a later upgrade and not part of the challenge steps.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Trading Combine <span class="text-xs font-normal text-emerald-600">&mdash; Evaluation Step</span></p>
      <p>Traders are evaluated in a simulated environment with specific profit and risk targets, paying a monthly fee based on account size and path chosen.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Express Funded Account <span class="text-xs font-normal text-emerald-600">&mdash; Payouts Begin Here</span></p>
      <p>After passing the Trading Combine, traders earn real profits. On the Standard path, a $149 activation fee applies. On the No Activation Fee path, there is no activation fee.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Live Funded Account <span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-500">&mdash; Later Upgrade</span></p>
      <p>A later upgrade from Express Funded, not a required challenge step. Provides access to live capital with stricter rules.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Two Paths ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Trading Combine Paths</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">
    Topstep now offers two paths for the Trading Combine: <strong>Standard</strong> and <strong>No Activation Fee</strong>. The Standard path has a lower monthly fee but charges a $149 activation fee when you reach Express Funded. The No Activation Fee path has a higher monthly fee but no activation fee when funded.
  </p>

  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-10">
    <table class="w-full text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
      <thead class="bg-slate-800 text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wide">
        <tr>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Account Size</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Standard (monthly)</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">No Activation Fee (monthly)</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Activation Fee</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Profit Target</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Max Loss Limit</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Daily Loss Limit</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$50K</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$49/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$109/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$149 (Standard only)</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$3,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$2,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$1,000</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-slate-50">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$100K</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$99/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$159/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$149 (Standard only)</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$6,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$3,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$1,500</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$150K</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$149/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$209/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$149 (Standard only)</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$9,000</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$4,500</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-700">$2,000</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- TRADING COMBINE DETAILS                                         -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs font-black flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Topstep Trading Combine
    </h3>

    <p class="mb-3">
      The Trading Combine is the <strong>only evaluation step</strong>. Traders must hit profit targets while staying within daily loss limits and maximum loss limits. The Trading Combine has <strong>no time limits</strong>.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-2 mb-4">
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-2">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold">Profit Target</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">$3K / $6K / $9K</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-2">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold">Max Loss Limit</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">$2K / $3K / $4.5K</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-2">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold">Time Limit</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-emerald-600">Unlimited</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Consistency Target -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4 mb-5">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">Topstep Consistency Target</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-800 mb-2">
        The Consistency Target ensures traders do not rely on one highly profitable day to pass. Profits must be spread across multiple sessions.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-800">
        <strong>Best Day Profit &divide; Overall Profit = Best Day % of Total Profit</strong>. No more than <strong>50%</strong> of total profits can come from one day.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Personal Daily Loss -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4 mb-5">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">TopstepX Personal Daily Loss Limit</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-700">
        On the TopstepX platform, all new or reset accounts can set a <strong>Personal Daily Loss Limit</strong> based on risk tolerance. This applies to TopstepX accounts only; the standard daily loss limits remain in place for other platforms.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 border border-emerald-200 p-4 mb-5">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold text-emerald-800 uppercase tracking-wide mb-1">Best Suited For</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-emerald-700">Futures traders who value a no-pressure evaluation with unlimited time, and the choice between Standard and No Activation Fee paths.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- EXPRESS FUNDED ACCOUNT                                          -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 text-white text-xs font-black flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Express Funded Account
    </h3>

    <p class="mb-3">
      After passing the Trading Combine, traders move to the Express Funded Account where <strong>payouts begin</strong>. On the Standard path, a one-time <strong>$149 activation fee</strong> applies. On the No Activation Fee path, there is <strong>no activation fee</strong>.
    </p>

    <p class="mb-4">
      Traders can choose between two payout paths: <strong>Standard</strong> and <strong>Consistency</strong>.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Standard Payout Path</p>
        <p>Requires <strong>5 winning days</strong> (each at $150+ Net P&L on the new dashboard). Payout requests capped at up to <strong>$5,000</strong>, limited to up to 50% of account balance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Consistency Payout Path</p>
        <p>Can qualify with <strong>3 days</strong> and a <strong>40% consistency target</strong>. Payout requests capped at up to <strong>$6,000</strong>, limited to up to 50% of account balance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Post-Payout Warning -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-red-200 bg-red-50 p-4 mb-5">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-red-900 mb-1">After First Payout</p>
      <p class="text-sm text-red-800">
        After the first payout in Express Funded, the <strong>Maximum Loss Limit is set to $0</strong>. This means any loss below your starting balance after payout will result in account closure.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Scaling Plan -->
    <h4 class="text-base font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Topstep Scaling Plan</h4>
    <p class="mb-3">
      Topstep's scaling plan manages position sizes by account. A $50K account is limited to <strong>5 lots</strong>, $100K to <strong>10 lots</strong>, and $150K to <strong>15 lots</strong>.
    </p>
    <p class="mb-5">
      Your balance is recalculated at the beginning of each trading day at 5:00pm CST. Opening too many lots can result in suspension, though Topstep allows a <strong>10-second window</strong> to correct errors.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 mb-5">
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-2 text-center">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold">$50K Account</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">5 lots max</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-2 text-center">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold">$100K Account</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">10 lots max</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-2 text-center">
        <p class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide font-semibold">$150K Account</p>
        <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-800">15 lots max</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <!-- LIVE FUNDED ACCOUNT                                             -->
  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <div class="mb-10">
    <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-7 h-7 rounded-full bg-slate-400 text-white text-xs font-black flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
      Live Funded Account <span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-500">(Later Upgrade)</span>
    </h3>

    <p class="mb-3">
      The Live Funded Account is a <strong>later upgrade</strong> from Express Funded &mdash; it is not part of the challenge steps. Traders access real capital with stricter rules.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-3 mb-5">
      <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Daily Payouts</p>
        <p>After <strong>30 winning trading days</strong> in the Live Funded Account, traders can request daily payouts up to <strong>100% of account balance</strong>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Trading Rules ───────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Trading Rules</h3>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-8">
    <table class="w-full text-sm">
      <thead class="bg-slate-50 text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wide">
        <tr>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Rule</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-center">Status</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-slate-900">News Trading</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center"><span class="text-emerald-600 font-bold">&#10003;</span> <span class="text-slate-600">Permitted (caution advised)</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-slate-50">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-slate-900">Weekend / Overnight Holding</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center"><span class="text-red-400 font-bold">&#10007;</span> <span class="text-slate-600">Positions closed by 3:10 PM CT daily</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-slate-900">Spoofing / Ultra-High-Speed</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center"><span class="text-red-400 font-bold">&#10007;</span> <span class="text-slate-600">Prohibited</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-slate-50">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium text-slate-900">System Manipulation</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-center"><span class="text-red-400 font-bold">&#10007;</span> <span class="text-slate-600">Prohibited &mdash; may lead to account closure</span></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <!-- Verdict -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-emerald-500 bg-emerald-50/60 px-5 py-4">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-1">Verdict on Topstep Funded Accounts</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      Topstep's evaluation is a single step &mdash; the Trading Combine &mdash; with no time limits and two paths to choose from (Standard and No Activation Fee). The Express Funded Account is where payouts begin, with Standard and Consistency payout paths offering flexibility. Traders should note that after the first payout, the Maximum Loss Limit is set to $0, and the Live Funded Account is a later upgrade rather than a required step.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>
)}

{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* SPREADS / COMMISSION FEES AND PRICING SECTION                       */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "spreads" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-3">
    Topstep operates exclusively within <strong>futures markets</strong>, so there are no spreads. However, multiple layers of fees apply depending on the platform, exchange, and stage of the programme.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-6">
    <strong>TopstepX</strong> is the lowest-cost platform option, though exchange and regulatory fees still apply on all platforms.
  </p>

  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Trading Combine Fees</p>
      <p>Monthly challenge fee + per-trade fees (commission, clearing, and exchange fees) + potential platform subscription costs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Express Funded Fees</p>
      <p>Activation fee (Standard path: $149; No Activation Fee path: $0) + per-trade fees + potential platform subscription costs.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Live Funded Fees</p>
      <p>Topstep pays for one market data feed. Traders pay monthly data fees only for <strong>additional feeds</strong>. Platform subscription costs may also apply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─── Trading Combine Fees ────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Trading Combine Fees by Path</h3>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-6">
    <table class="w-full text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
      <thead class="bg-slate-800 text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wide">
        <tr>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-left">Account Size</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">Standard Path</th>
          <th class="px-4 py-3 text-right">No Activation Fee Path</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$50K</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$49/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$109/month</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-slate-50">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$100K</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$99/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$159/month</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="bg-white">
          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">$150K</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$149/month</td>
          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right text-slate-900">$209/month</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <p class="mb-6">
    Per-trade fees vary by platform. TopstepX has the lowest cost ($0.04 + exchange fees per round turn). Other platforms range from $1.52 to $2.04+ per round turn depending on commission, clearing, and data fees.
  </p>

  <!-- ─── Live Funded Data Fees ──────────────────────────────────── -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Live Funded Account &mdash; Additional Fees</h3>
  <div class="space-y-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Market Data Feeds</p>
      <p>Topstep pays for <strong>one market data feed</strong>. Traders pay monthly data fees only for <strong>additional feeds</strong> beyond the first.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 p-4">
      <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-1">Depth of Market (Level 2) Data <span class="text-xs font-normal text-slate-500">$34.25/month</span></p>
      <p>For traders who require more detailed market data, Level 2 Depth of Market data is available for <strong>$34.25 per month</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Platform Selection Note -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 p-4 mb-6">
    <p class="text-sm font-bold text-amber-900 mb-1">Important: Platform Selection</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-amber-800">
      Once you begin the Trading Combine, switching platforms may be limited. <strong>Rithmic</strong> platforms (NinjaTrader, ATAS) can switch between each other. <strong>CQG</strong> platforms (Tradovate, TradingView) can switch within CQG. <strong>TopstepX</strong> is isolated &mdash; switching to any other platform requires starting a new Trading Combine.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Verdict -->
  <div class="rounded-xl border-l-4 border-emerald-500 bg-emerald-50/60 px-5 py-4">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-800 mb-1">Verdict on Commissions &amp; Pricing</p>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
      Topstep's fee structure varies by platform and stage. TopstepX offers the lowest per-trade costs, though exchange and regulatory fees still apply. The two Trading Combine paths (Standard and No Activation Fee) give traders flexibility in how they manage upfront costs. In the Live Funded Account, Topstep covers one data feed, with traders paying only for additional feeds &mdash; a change from the older blanket per-exchange pricing.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>
)}

{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{/* MARKETS / FUTURES MARKETS AND LEVERAGE SECTION                      */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "markets" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-3">
    Topstep provides access to <strong>32 different futures markets</strong> across forex, equity indices, oil and gas, metals, and agricultural commodities &mdash; all CME Group products.
  </p>
  <p class="mb-6">
    Trading fees vary depending on the platform used. Maximum position sizes are defined by the scaling plan: <strong>5 lots</strong> ($50K), <strong>10 lots</strong> ($100K), and <strong>15 lots</strong> ($150K).
  </p>

  <!-- Forex Futures -->
  <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Forex Futures</h3>
  <p class="mb-4">8 forex futures markets including major currencies and micro counterparts.</p>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-slate-200 mb-8">
    <table class="w-full text-sm whitespace-nowrap">
      <thead class="bg-slate-800 text-xs font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-wide">
        <tr><th class="px-3 py-3 text-left">Product</th><th class="px-3 py-3 text-center">TopstepX</th><th class="px-3 py-3 text-center">Tradovate / TV</th><th class="px-3 py-3 text-center">NinjaTrader / Rithmic</th><th class="px-3 py-3 text-center">T4</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
        <tr class="bg-white"><td class="px-3 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-900">Australian Dollar (6A)</td><td class="px-3 py-3 text-center">$3.24</td><td class="px-3 py-3 text-center">$4.72</td><td class="px-3 py-3 text-center">$4.80</td><td class="px-3 py-3 text-center">$5.24</td></tr>
